                         "text":  "### Summary Official contact points for waterârelated enquiries, emergencies, and payments. ### Department Contacts | Service | Phone | Email | Location | |---------|-------|-------|----------| | General Enquiries \u0026 Billing | 0800 1234 (tollâfree) | water.billing@harare.gov.zw | Selous Avenue, Harare | | New Connections \u0026 Applications | +263 242 752123 | water.connections@harare.gov.zw | Rowland Square, CBD | | Emergency Water Outages | 0800 1234 or 0712 345 678 (WhatsApp) | water.emergency@harare.gov.zw | 24/7 | | Meter Readings \u0026 Faults | +263 242 752124 | water.meter@harare.gov.zw | Morton Jaffray office | | Complaints \u0026 Feedback | +263 242 752125 | water.complaints@harare.gov.zw | Customer Service Centre, Mbare | ### Zonal Water Offices (for local issues) | Zone | Areas Covered | Phone | |------|---------------|-------| | Zone 1 | CBD, Mbare, Sunningdale | +263 242 752201 | | Zone 4 | Budiriro, Glen View, Mufakose | +263 242 752204 | | Zone 5 | Kambuzuma, Kuwadzana, Dzivarasekwa | +263 242 752205 | ### Payment Locations - **Online:** pay.harare.gov.zw - **Mobile:** EcoCash biller 2020 (account number = water bill number) - **In person:** Any council cashier (CBD, Mbare, Budiriro, Highfield) ### Common Questions Answered - Q: What is the emergency number for a burst pipe in my street? A: Call 0800 1234, available 24/7. Provide your street name and nearest cross street. - Q: How do I get my water bill emailed to me? A: Send an email to water.billing@harare.gov.zw with your account number and request eâbilling.",
